Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:11.58,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1\blur3\fs23}翻译 浅荷 十八 斑马线  校译 洛艾妖 时间 仓鼠  后期 风 压制 风 追忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我在你身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克痛苦的时候我来保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难过的时候我陪你一起哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以不要丢下我一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不会丢下你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到这个世界的终结 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:11.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Do you kill your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:16.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you can fulfill your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you die for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.35,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.92,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Life is a game  It's a survival  That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.51,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Time and Space  It's a crossroad  through a gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:33.14,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Where do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.54,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you need to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:42.91,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.78,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.79,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.82,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:55.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh,We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:56.29,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:08:01.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.96,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:13.83,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 就劳烦您大驾到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 爸爸他 居然骗了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 他们打算到上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上面？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定有办法逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}7/7 12:45[樱见塔 第一了望台] 由乃从7th那里夺回了手机。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}7/7 12:48[樱见塔 第一了望台] 发生爆炸。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用降落伞逃脱？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}7/7 13:02[樱见塔 第一了望台] 7th他们拖着爸爸去了第二了望台。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:09:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 我们就打倒他们夺走降落伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次你不是都输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在还受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我们失败的原因显而易见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小雪的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是二对一 所以输了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 走吧 然后一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只要按照自己的方法去做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fad(400,0)}同时 “儿童养护设施 母亲之家”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 樱见塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为发生了莫名其妙的爆炸起火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都有倒塌的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且天野雪辉的病床上也留有“我们去樱见塔”的字条
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子可能会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去联系雪辉的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 8th的“服务器”也没有找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这边完全是个诱饵？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克 他们追来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才说不要管什么1st 赶快把未来日记破坏掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 看到软弱的家伙 就不自觉地管起闲事来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能在这座塔举行婚礼太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们永远都会在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要彻底把他们打垮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的爱怎么可能输给他们那种虚伪的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st这次差不多也反省了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次估计会拚死一搏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们走吧 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 马克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2nd？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太弱了 所以我藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我输的理由只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我暴露在危险的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有在反省！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我上了 7th！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我上了 7th！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我上了”？你不是躲起来了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\pos(391,88)\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0}马克和2nd开战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(621,146)}刀从右边向着脸刺来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(456,194)}小心啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(370,217)}马克抓住了2nd
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(460,329)}这样的话只剩下1st了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(642,351)}不愧是马克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz354.009\c&H607458&\3c&HC9D4CF&\shad0\pos(384,357)}马克发现了1st的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克 刀从右边向脸刺来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃！他会从右边向你踢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是我这边的刀快！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊透顶 别小看人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}7/7 13:00　小雪在父亲和我之前选择了我！今天说不定是我人生中最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}7/7 13:10 小雪在广播室里给我加油诶。我一定会好好努力给你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}7/7 13:20 小雪在广播室里。要好好的躲在那里哦。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}7/7 13:30 小雪被7th抓住了！怎么办，得去救他！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}7/7 13:40 小雪跟7th对战，受伤了。得赶紧治疗。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st在广播室么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把他抓回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的… 你们还真是不长教训呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二对一怎么可能赢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 二对一不可能会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！1st！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是日记显示确实在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这个手机是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二对一是赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这个是我们所准备的假手机！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}13:20 爱因被1st用飞镖破坏手机而死。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞镖？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如由乃的作战一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 快躲开飞镖！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被躲开了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是糟透了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:14:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天只会比今天更好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克把最糟变成了最好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马…克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这个降落伞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人就可以从塔里逃出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可以得到小雪的夸奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要夺取日记不就足够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这家伙想杀了小雪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的做法老是这么极端！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 这样就可以从这里逃出去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 结果还是没能破坏掉手机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话借款还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九郎 你在做什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪怎么样了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被最麻烦的家伙抓到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想办法脱身的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你带我去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去警局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不知道小雪发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在一起吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问过警察了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！ 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了放开我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 完全抬不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾呢 马克已经从塌方里逃脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}13：10 马克和2nd战斗 右边方向会有小刀飞向脑袋 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}13: 20 马克抓住了2nd 就只剩下1st了 不愧是马克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}13:30 马克找到了1st藏身的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}13:40 马克从塌方的地方逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}13:50 马克好像受伤了 必须尽早包扎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的情况已经通过日记传达给了外面的马克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我快要死了的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你们将葬身于这塔下的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克马上就会从这脱身的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 就是马克的胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你剁碎然后把外面的男人引进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会把这里挖开的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别阻止我 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下这一条路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么做了也无济于事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就把你救出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是要成为神 永远在一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么我都要保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 马克 反正我都要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这样很好 继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人是人质
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是让她住手的问题吧 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不弄脏自己的手 只会让2nd保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么要人道之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的话还真是不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我抬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 你给我在下面推一下啊 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是7th
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就正中由乃下怀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在不断地保护你 杀死敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想把脏活累活都推到2nd身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 2nd你也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少对我发号施令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么要保护1st
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却任意地扭曲1st的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不算是协助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自私
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该适可而止的是你 你这臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我是受到威胁才做这些的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我 我从一开始就没想要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了 我马上就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就会死？ 跟我没有关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西 给老子滚一边去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我们的“爱”和你们的“爱”相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也中枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人一起把它抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃你是真的喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是在暴走？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在缺乏信心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我信心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有赶上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz27.325\pos(604,372)\c&H4F5F4B&\3c&HCDDED4&\shad0}7th 美神 爱失血过多身亡 DEAD END
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7th
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对敌人流露怜悯的眼神 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为神 两人永远在一起的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an8}7th 美神爱 失血过多身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an8)}马克来救我了 果然还是马克最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也算是永远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会和爸爸妈妈好好说下的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能会讨厌爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有各种各样的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我希望爸爸妈妈重归于好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望由乃能帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪辉君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西岛警官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 雪辉君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 在这个现场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西岛警官好像说了点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已经听不进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}(妈妈死了。)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪辉君 你的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:42.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あとどのぐらい失えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:42.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还将失去几何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:48.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高鳴る鼓動を許される
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:48.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份悸动才将被允许
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:53.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　焚くって涙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:53.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 焚烧之泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:22:59.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　降れるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:22:59.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 如将滑落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:05.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全ては未来の繋ぐ鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:05.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都为紧系未来之锁匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:12.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れる体に傷目感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:12.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于崩坏之身中觉察那心伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:21.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度　君を　守ると
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:21.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将再次 守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:24.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:24.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此立誓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4/21 18:00 [樱见市内某租赁公寓]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱着你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.38,0:23:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我洗好了 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.90,0:23:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也去洗……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:23:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老子才不知道她是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪根葱啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？ 我是使魔之女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.45,0:24:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简称 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.39,0:24:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔女？！　马克！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要用这么引人误会的简称好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马克终究也只不过是个下半身思考的野兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.03,0:24:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 我才不认识这女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.95,0:24:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给相亲相爱的你们准备了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.31,0:24:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‘交换日记’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.83,0:24:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是能让你们俩人知晓对方未来的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.83,0:24:32.97,Note1,,0000,0000,0000,,4/21 18:40\N我知道了马克没有劈腿。果然还是马克最好了！\N4/21 19:23\N跑到阳台外面突然有只猫飞扑过来。马克，救命啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.33,0:24:32.97,Note2,,0000,0000,0000,,4/21 18:40\N爱解开了对我的误会。不愧是本大爷的女人。真有一套！\N4/21 19:23\N爱被猫缠住了。没办法，就让本大爷来保护你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.50,0:24:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是马克最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.47,0:24:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我眼中就只有你了 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.82,0:24:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这俩人的爱到底是深还是浅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.85,0:24:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.73,0:24:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的男人和女人还真是复杂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.23,0:24:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不再通关一次游戏来复习下呐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.48,0:25:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}串线

